## 1. Panoramica

TIRO è una piattaforma gestionale aziendale unificata, costruita su componenti open source selezionati e integrati, progettata per centralizzare tutte le fonti di informazione aziendale (email, WhatsApp, chiamate, documenti), strutturarle in un database operativo e azionabile, e alimentare un layer agentico AI che simula la struttura organizzativa dell'azienda. Il sistema è concepito come prodotto multi-tenant, adattabile a realtà aziendali diverse, e pensato per essere scalabile e personalizzabile per ogni cliente che lo adotti. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/attachments/148535006/29efe48c-e7ed-4fac-a51c-1b1b143684cb/trascrizione.txt?AWSAccessKeyId=ASIA2F3EMEYE5RJF25CW&Signature=4iBBdFFn7tOOkI9yLVnqEZsor%2Bg%3D&x-amz-security-token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEA0aCXVzLWVhc3QtMSJHMEUCIBmoXMh92WZ6WxDkDYSwWCgwb1mbjx9mT5takQkm460iAiEAzswtY4Yr%2BEXpLgJ6kUU0TEx%2FkmlfLojlOOZZnSEzC8kq%2FAQI1v%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARABGgw2OTk3NTMzMDk3MDUiDI80Xh2HELpP56AlsSrQBDFh%2BHTzKGtfXJvqOEcQ1fPHVhbaHW%2FBSupWsf2du3KB3z2aJ20rVnyNz0%2B9fNu4A4u7i0LknjvjJUyj2Nh9TY1e0hezFc4jr04UrKVz9iDQek8RkxWT3AYXdt8Xgb2JBPpA9GOW2S4SHYV5ztnHY8crCw38SuYP8%2BNDkI1qD1gZkthjUs0h%2F906M4gA2W1J1yU%2FXWeenN0mN8RsOLZFLAPNhavxQN%2BpEgCAbqEWhCbkQv3hY4V%2Bf%2FjcyPzYddlgifOS%2Fkg48tZ%2FdRi%2FTphLY3FWu8XBdhUup1WlLst3k7ZBRvKU7PnPsYPjUsYGE72diITFCL7WYiWCCAG79xgXjpvKp88tr7Az2EZ7oPLhYU%2FxrnLua%2F7U1i5V4DqIHPc4HZO983Ydgt4j1evHfTypNdDXoNHd2G0LxOR9cAPi6k9XcRFLA%2FxmlsCsJd7Zex95VgtUypPCIjUQc2G8hDdH1xXVL2mGm4q1qZ4dqpSGVaNjdl%2B6resTt9EmTs4xZ1tdUUBrZbcZq6Pw8TR66gl3cuSEy2BkPnzjWe7YyUmbzVJ6WPmuRtOpM1Ey9GQpsbTk78bEwTMXVEQ42vFtFtvv36jSJaiiT2qKPZBPn1nUJ8Sa1cD21CORR%2FhiAlBZbgu13ZogobXDuqu4TnypsVfHtWyjkuemIvW8uTHVMunGseHSRXFpEppSZTAgmsDxoz0jrsFrTS1gSjqOBeAg%2FUX3YXGr7tARKknxKGIDYiL3iGeuiEuQ3epXZkJrEuJ%2FVH0Qy2H%2FkAvhhneyFVlgUwCV25AwnrzQzgY6mAHYRLqc%2BkVwVL7G1G7zmkqpVRa2uzXZ3PbxpvubV9fXG6eUJgT%2FryZ6Cs2NV6k2Mh2Yk7kLFi48x0gHx0534ZHHj7qng%2BTlWpYskw0QlTjlfH1eZUJo7lNdA370v%2BK